snippet.title: Azura Cecillia Ch.
snippet.description:
Ohazura, earthlings! Nice to meet you.

My name is Azura Cecillia, a soldier from outer space. I'm a Virtual YouTuber and I like to play video games. If you're bored, feel free to come and watch my streams. Let's chat a lot and be friends! 

(Facebook)
https://www.facebook.com/AzuraCecillia/

(Twitter)
https://twitter.com/Azura_Cecillia
